      <h3>Message from comittee</h3>
        This year’s youth camp is themed “…YET NOT I”: HIS WORK, HIS GRACE, OUR CALLING,
1 Corinthians 15:10- “But by the grace of God I am what I am, and his grace to me was not without
effect. No, I worked harder than all of them-yet not I, but the grace of God that was with me.” This
