All in all, my testimonies from camp are numerous and I believe strongly that this year, during Youth Camp 2017, it'll be business as usual with
  God touching each and everyone's life in one way or the other. Just come with a willing heart and your testimony will be great!

 <div class="name">Enam Kunutsor</div>
